ll not regret it. This will be a new chapter in our life and we look forward to the challenge. Our kids think we are going through our second childhood. What a great second childhood it will be. </td></tr></table><table border=0 cellpadding=5 width="100%" class='ubut'><tr><td width=150 valign=top><div class='bsmall'><a name="c1271167169"><b>Comment 20</b></a><br><b>04/13/10 09:59</b><br><div style='font-size: 12pt;'><b><b><a href="http://board.panamatotal.com/profiles/Glen_2" rel="author">Glen</a></b></b></div><div><ul class='star-rating'><li class='current-rating' style='width:37px;'></li></ul></div>International Citizen :-)<br><div onclick='return loginnow(4)'><img src="http://xp.loszona.com/xml/contact.png" width=75 height=16></div><script type="text/javascript">
